introduction description.defaults: This library aims to help you use the Bulma CSS Framework in your React project

instalation description.defaults: The easiest way to install React Bulma Components its using npm.

usage description.defaults: Currently there are two ways to use this library depending of your needs and configuration

basic instalation subtitle.defaults: This configuration will allow you to start fast with minimum configuration but with less customization and no treeshaking by default (will include all components)

basic instalation description.defaults: After the instalation you need to include the already transpiled bulma css, and you can start importing the component you need from the basic folder.
